#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/zfs/_index.adoc:2694
msgid ""
"This expands the kernel address space, allowing the `vm.kvm_size` tunable to "
"be pushed beyond the currently imposed limit of 1 GB, or the limit of 2 GB "
"for PAE.  To find the most suitable value for this option, divide the "
"desired address space in megabytes by four.  In this example, it is `512` "
"for 2 GB."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ====
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/zfs/_index.adoc:2695
